title: WTF! BIDEN IS MAKING YOU PAY FOR WORTHLESS COLLEGE DEGREES!
description: Is it a border crisis or a border invasion? And can you call it a "crisis" when it's working exactly how the people who control Joe Biden want it to? These are the questions answered on today's show. We'll also have a legal update on the Trump raid. And don't look now, but Joe Biden is planning to bail out student loan borrowers AGAIN with YOUR tax dollars.
